title: Ken Tamplin Discography 1987-2003 (12 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
KEN TAMPLIN DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 12 releases...

 * 1987 - Demos - With Joshua
 * 1990 - An Axe To Grind
 * 1991 - Soul Survivor
 * 1994 - Tamplin
 * 1995 - In The Witness Box
 * 1995 - We The People
 * 1995 - We The People - European Release
 * 1997 - Liquid Music 1 Compilation
 * 1997 - The Colors Of Christmas
 * 1999 - Brave Days Of Old
 * 2001 - Where Love Is
 * 2003 - Wake The Nations

Ken Tamplin is an American Christian rock performer and vocal coach. Tamplin is known for his vocal range and has composed music for television and movies.

Be Blessed,
